user.canProvide: Anything investing-related and helping companies go 0-1. Also love chatting about career development and growth.
user.intro:
I'm a Partner with Contrary on the early-stage team. I originally joined as a Venture Partner at Penn while getting my MBA/MA and am now on the full-time team. 

Prior to Contrary, I founded two companies (one in surplus food, one in enterprise SaaS for office management) and was a fractional COO doing growth/ops consulting work for early-stage organizations. I also previously spent time as a consultant with PwC and doing vaccine market access work with the Clinton Health Access Initiative. 

I went to Yale for undergrad, studying economics and English.
user.lookingFor: Meet more of the Contrary community - please reach out!
user.meetWithBlurb: Happy to chat about anything investing-related and helping companies go 0-1. Also love chatting about career development and growth.
